description: Number of monic irreducible polynomials over GF(5) with fixed nonzero trace.
comments: Also number of 5-ary Lyndon words with trace 1 mod 5; trace 2 mod 5; trace 3 mod 5; trace 4 mod 5; also number of 5-ary Lyndon words of trace 1 over GF(5), trace 2 over GF(5); trace 3 over GF(5); trace 4 over GF(5).
